data.description: Welcome Home to this spacious 4 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 story home. Large eat in kitchen boasts a large kitchen island/breakfast bar. Main floor laundry room features a large storage closet to make laundry a breeze. Full unfinished basement offers plenty of room for extra storage.  A little sweat equity will give this darling home a fresh, new feel.  Make an appointment before it is too late.  A/C new within last 5 years.  New water heater installed in 2023. Rm Sizes and SQFT are estimated, not guaranteed to be correct.
